welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Tarboro, the charming town known for its historic buildings and Southern hospitality. We invite you to explore and discover all that this quaint city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Rocky Mount-wilson Airport handles all commercial flights and services.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Rocky Mount-wilson Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
